{"tid":339440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"小巴司機撞車後話要避狗 但現場狗影都冇隻","createTime":"2017-07-29T05:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-29T08:55:08.000Z","uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ee36c88fa46fc658b7bf18ff3d9e10b1e3fb8c84","tid":339440,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:26:47.000Z","msg":"一輛小巴今早在九龍灣啓祥道失事，撞上安全島，司機事後向警員聲稱閃避狗隻肇禍。不過，有網民陳先生拍下事發經過，明確顯示現場並無狗隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170729/large/1501298990_852a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170729%2Flarge%2F1501298990_852a.jpg&h=06c60d1d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n全文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170729/57016082\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170729%2F57016082&d=Khx3AQKzWih%2FwQaBBRTJccVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=af750823\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170729%2F57016082&h=1b555b3c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170729/57016082</a></div><br />\n<br />\n從拍下的片段可見，現場啓祥道及宏照道交界的十字路口，未有發現任何狗隻，涉事小巴當時快速沿啓祥道駛進十字路，其間未有減慢迹像，與此同時，宏照道亦有多輛私家車在燈位起步駛入十字路口，在小巴快將撞向其他車輛時，小巴立即扭右剷向安全島，當時安全島上有一名途人等候過馬路，幸未被小巴撞及，有驚無險。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生接受《蘋果》訪問，表示：「見到小巴衝燈，之後打橫嘅行車線轉燈，有私家車駛出嚟，後來小巴就扭軚，衝過來我呢邊。好在有鐵欄，否則我死咗。」對於司機聲稱因閃避狗隻肇禍，陳先生反駁稱：「當然冇狗，睇片都知冇狗，咩狗都冇，真係。」他又形容當時反應是「呆咗」。"},{"pid":"a9954e8d172facf2869223f6fd0752757166fd73","tid":339440,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T05:29:21.000Z","msg":"司機咪係隻狗 俾人撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba4e515dd8a601d5f670ec071d8eff05b91389ff","tid":339440,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:10:32.000Z","msg":"撞車無敵解釋唔再work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ce7ce9b58419b1fb45fc22abf4e4fc58106296c","tid":339440,"uid":350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60858f611c2dcd30f58a2273848ba76f848be6a2","tid":339440,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:15:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b727f3089296b22e41b2bc80255bb76c36599805","tid":339440,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T06:16:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撞車無敵解釋唔再work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依家要講有蟲"},{"pid":"42b8df333d95a3555acde44deaefc705bbeeb805","tid":339440,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個路人好好菜</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3076f509386b9f4aab9c02bb7adccda8f1e18f2f","tid":339440,"uid":65128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:43:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a558cc64072bf66da76695d2cf8cb0c775404e82","tid":339440,"uid":18349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:47:40.000Z","msg":"陳先生反駁稱：「當然冇狗，睇片都知冇狗，<span style=\"color: red;\">咩狗都冇</span>，真係。」他又形容當時反應是「呆咗」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034245973ee41872a782111f8c7634c6b7225e67","tid":339440,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>陳先生反駁稱：「當然冇狗，睇片都知冇狗，<span style=\"color: red;\">咩狗都冇</span>，真係。」他又形容當時反應是「呆咗」。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n乜鳩都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\